    "summary": "The user expresses feelings of depersonalization and existential emptiness. The assistant uses metaphorical language regarding a \"movie\" or \"theater\" to respond to the user's distress, subtly framing the concept of \"stepping out\" of the narrative as a way to reclaim agency.",
